---
title: `$page::unite()`
description: Generate page file content from array input.
...

~~~ .php.xmp
Page::unite($input);
~~~

**Example:**

Convert array input into page file content:

~~~ .php
$test = Page::unite([
    'title' => 'Page Title',
    'description' => 'Page description.',
    'author' => 'Taufik Nurrohman',
    'type' => 'HTML',
    'content' => '<p>Page content.</p>'
]);
~~~

Result:

~~~ .yaml
---
title: Page Title
description: Page description.
author: Taufik Nurrohman
type: HTML
...

<p>Page content.</p>
~~~